Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.35,0:00:04.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,終於
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.06,0:00:06.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,終於
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.65,0:00:12.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,爸媽終於給我買手機了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:00.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,——op——
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.16,0:01:46.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,手機
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.79,0:01:49.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,保存好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.13,0:01:51.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.38,0:01:52.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.89,0:02:02.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你買手機了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.43,0:02:03.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.93,0:02:05.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那是最新款嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:08.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我也正準備要買這款
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.65,0:02:09.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我可以摸摸看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:10.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.07,0:02:14.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 還挺輕的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.28,0:02:17.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為了今天絞盡腦汁才想出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:20.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,用手機捉弄高木同學的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.87,0:02:24.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天我就要用它戰勝高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.75,0:02:28.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誒 原來是這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:31.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.38,0:02:32.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:42.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.64,0:02:43.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.97,0:02:45.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.90,0:03:01.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我原本以為高木同學會問我要郵箱地址
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:03.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.87,0:03:04.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.79,0:03:07.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.91,0:03:11.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:13.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣下去就沒法實施計劃了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:21.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我主動去問高木同學不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:25.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼我沒有注意到這麼簡單的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:26.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:28.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:29.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.90,0:03:35.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,把你的郵箱地址…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:39.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,抱歉 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.70,0:03:44.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 我為什麼要這麼緊張 冷靜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:48.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,只是找高木同學要她的郵箱地址而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.50,0:03:54.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道我正在問女生要郵箱地址嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:03:59.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感覺這樣…有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.67,0:04:02.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,像是那個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:04.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我說 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.39,0:04:07.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你有什麼事情想要問我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:08.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:09.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.97,0:04:10.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:19.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我還以為你想問我要郵箱地址呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:21.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.65,0:04:24.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 不如說這正是機會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:26.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個問題只要回答Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.78,0:04:28.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我就能拿到她的郵箱地址了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:30.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你大意了啊 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.67,0:04:36.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,其實你說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.00,0:04:37.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那你剛才為什麼要糊弄過去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:39.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道你害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.42,0:04:41.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:43.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.22,0:04:47.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 才不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:53.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:55.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是有什麼事 連繫起來就方便多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.69,0:04:56.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,例如呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:58.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是有什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:05:01.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你還問到了誰的郵箱地址
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:06.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,木村和高尾 還有中井
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.91,0:05:07.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,其他的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:10.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,還沒問
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:13.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒錯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:15.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學是我問的第一個女生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:18.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,所以快點 快點把郵箱地址告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:23.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你想和我交換郵箱地址嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.34,0:05:30.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才沒有 我只是想用郵件來捉弄高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:32.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才不是像你想的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:35.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我真的一點奇怪的事情都沒有想過…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:47.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我就知道會是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:57.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,雖然你想捉弄我的計劃泡湯了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:05:59.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但我們還是來交換郵箱地址吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:07.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.35,0:06:11.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,作為捉弄我的賠禮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:14.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你下週要幫我值日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.89,0:06:16.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我才沒有捉弄你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.60,0:06:18.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,還沒捉弄到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.94,0:06:22.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是 如果沒暴露的話就會捉弄我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.98,0:06:25.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那就這麼定了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:31.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在這之前 我們到家再聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:38.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在這之前？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.88,0:06:45.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道我在家裡也會被她捉弄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.97,0:06:50.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,想要手機
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:54.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是昨天和媽媽說的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.89,0:06:57.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她說我要買手機還太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:07:00.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這麼突然她肯定會這樣說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.48,0:07:02.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你無論幹什麼都很突然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.44,0:07:04.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才不突然好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:06.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我很久以前就想要了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:08.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,很久以前是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.86,0:07:10.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:14.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,大概一週前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.16,0:07:18.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,看你這樣子 應該是三天前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:20.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,無論怎麼樣 都太突然了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.63,0:07:25.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}那是什麼呀 犯規了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:26.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:28.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}超級大狸貓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:34.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不過 現在有手機的同學也越來越多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:36.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我也有點想要了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:39.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對吧 你也想要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:42.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,大家一起去拜託媽媽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:44.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早苗也很想要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:46.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 我不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.15,0:07:48.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誒 為什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.03,0:07:50.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一起來發郵件嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:51.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:55.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為我已經有一部了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.53,0:07:58.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼你會有手機
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:01.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為社團有時會弄得很晚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:02.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,所以爸媽讓我帶著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:07.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,話說這種事情你倒是告訴我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:08.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:12.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是說早苗也有的話說不定就會買給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:14.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個主意不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:15.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我也這樣跟家裡說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:17.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣一來就能得到手機了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:19.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一起來發好多郵件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:22.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我想在睡覺前玩接龍或者猜謎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:25.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誒 好麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:28.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是因為你這麼說 你爸媽才不給你買的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.03,0:08:30.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我們來講恐怖故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:34.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你是最膽小的那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.66,0:08:35.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:38.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:39.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我們來試一試嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:45.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有天晚上 一個陌生的電話號碼打了進來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:47.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,接通電話的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:49.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,聽到的是一陣呻吟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:55.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,慌慌張張地把電話掛斷之後 對方卻再也沒有打過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:08:56.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.34,0:08:59.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是因為太過在意 試著回撥了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:00.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誒 為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:04.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,然而 什麼聲音也沒有聽見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:06.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:07.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:12.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不知為何 電話費竟高達十萬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:16.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an7}「架空請求」，日本的電信詐騙的一種
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:16.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太可怕了 電信詐騙太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.57,0:09:19.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明明是由加莉更可怕好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:25.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,恐怖故事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:33.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早上好 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.67,0:09:35.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.38,0:09:38.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你遵守之前的約定了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:40.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:47.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我來幫你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.06,0:09:48.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:09:58.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你好像很睏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:01.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:07.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你熬夜看了錄下來的百分百單相思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:08.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:09.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.25,0:10:12.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那是為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:14.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有點事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.55,0:10:16.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,和班上的男生聊短信了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:19.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:20.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,聊了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.35,0:10:24.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咦 高木同學難得對這個話題感興趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:27.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:31.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,第一次有手機的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:33.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,和別人聊短信真的很開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:36.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我當時也是聊到不能自拔的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:40.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,然後 家人就叫我適可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:45.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,和高木同學聊短信的人 是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.71,0:10:48.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:50.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是和班上的女生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.33,0:10:51.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:57.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,冷靜 之前也有過這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.38,0:11:00.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,最後一次和我兩個人一起騎車的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.93,0:11:02.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是我爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:05.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.52,0:11:06.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是和你爸聊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:09.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我才不會和爸爸聊短信啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.23,0:11:11.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那倒也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:13.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你想知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:16.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:20.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是西片告訴我男孩子之間會聊些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.16,0:11:22.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我就告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.32,0:11:24.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:28.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:30.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我有個一石二鳥的好辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.33,0:11:36.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學 你也就只有現在能悠哉悠哉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.84,0:11:38.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,其實呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.22,0:11:43.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,昨天男生們互發有趣的視頻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:46.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎樣的視頻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.47,0:11:48.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,很好很好 如我所料
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.61,0:11:56.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這是木村發來的網址
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.54,0:12:14.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,把這個害我昨晚睡不好的視頻…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.63,0:12:20.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你給我發了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.59,0:12:24.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有可愛動物的視頻網站
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.09,0:12:26.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難不成是色情網站呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.60,0:12:27.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.43,0:12:33.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:35.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣啊高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:38.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,害怕得說不出話來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:41.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.90,0:12:44.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.66,0:12:47.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片你總是在看這種東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.16,0:12:52.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:53.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,等等 那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.75,0:12:57.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我給你發的不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:12:58.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我只是問一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.42,0:13:03.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好吧 看看西片給我發的視頻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.68,0:13:08.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,又是這樣 高木同學這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.31,0:13:12.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的是動物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.81,0:13:16.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真可愛啊 這個是山羊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:18.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,很好很好 她放鬆警惕了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:20.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,快到時間了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.95,0:13:25.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好 就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.11,0:13:26.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,被嚇得魂飛魄散吧 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:31.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.25,0:13:36.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不對 你不害怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.46,0:13:37.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:41.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為是在早上看的 所以也沒那麼害怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:46.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,確實是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.30,0:13:50.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,原來在發這種東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:52.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,男生真有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.39,0:13:57.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學會和誰聊天 聊些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:01.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我聊的只是普通的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:03.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣根本不算回答嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:04.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:06.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,讓我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:10.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對方名字的首字母是「i」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.16,0:14:10.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「i」？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.87,0:14:12.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「i」…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.25,0:14:15.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是石井同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.87,0:14:16.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:19.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「i」之後是「to」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:20.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「ito」…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.59,0:14:21.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「ito」？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:22.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼 是伊藤嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:24.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那個男生？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:26.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是班上的伊藤啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.34,0:14:30.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,然後 最後一個字是「ko」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:33.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「ito」…「ko」？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:33.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an7}日語中的「itoko」是指表或堂兄弟姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:36.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:46.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,九十七
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:48.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,九十…八
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.99,0:14:51.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,九十…九
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.24,0:14:54.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡的高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:57.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我還以為今天肯定能捉弄到她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.87,0:15:00.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,結果反過來被捉弄了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:06.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不行 今天還沒結束
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.09,0:15:11.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早上不奏效 晚上發給她就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:14.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,回家的時候木村發給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.31,0:15:16.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,更恐怖的視頻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:19.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,雖然因為太可怕了 我還沒看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:21.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就把這個發給高木同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:25.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.40,0:15:30.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不會又是什麼要讓我做俯臥撐的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:35.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喂 是西片嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:36.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.87,0:15:38.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我覺得差不多到時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:40.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:42.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,發恐怖視頻給我的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:45.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:48.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:52.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,以為這樣就能揭露我的計劃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.22,0:15:53.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,勝負還…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.22,0:15:56.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「你好好期待著掛斷電話之後會發生什麼吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:00.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你是這樣想的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.39,0:16:02.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 沒這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:04.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:05.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,千真萬確
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:11.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那你差不多要睡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:14.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 應該吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:16.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:19.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我也差不多要睡覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.33,0:16:21.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:27.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感覺有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:32.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我還是第一次在晚上和西片說話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:34.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有點小心動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.97,0:16:38.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那明天見 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:41.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:49.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.78,0:16:51.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.15,0:16:53.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你還沒掛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:55.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我說電話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.32,0:16:58.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學來掛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:01.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是我打給你的 西片來掛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:03.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:07.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我們數一二 一起掛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:08.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.25,0:17:09.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.17,0:17:14.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你個騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.63,0:17:16.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學才是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.07,0:17:36.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:38.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今晚也睡不著了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.45,0:17:41.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,照片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.42,0:17:47.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,貓在打架
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.29,0:17:50.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你等一會 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:52.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:54.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:56.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,保持這樣 保持這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.26,0:18:00.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好 按快門的好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.77,0:18:05.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡 只拍到了牆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.06,0:18:08.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你怎麼了 突然拍什麼照片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.36,0:18:15.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我們男生現在在比誰能拍出更有趣的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:18.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,現在第一名是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.08,0:18:23.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,木村的這張遙遙領先
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:27.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這張的衝擊感很強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.91,0:18:28.63,Takagisan-huamian,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs100\pos(500,212)}超市
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.91,0:18:28.63,Takagisan-huamian-1,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fn@楷体\an7\frz270\pos(592,722)}大狸貓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.25,0:18:31.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有趣的照片嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:36.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學 讓我拍拍你的鬼臉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.30,0:18:40.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那張絕對能比過超級大狸貓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.60,0:18:44.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是西片什麼都願意做的話就行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:47.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼都？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:49.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是什麼都答應我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:52.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.78,0:18:57.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明明這裡就有一位能衝擊第一名的種子選手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.49,0:18:59.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.87,0:19:06.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學 你的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:12.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明明給你拍照機會了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.88,0:19:14.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,再 再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.42,0:19:15.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:18.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:20.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她可是高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:22.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嚐到甜頭之後肯定還會再來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.18,0:19:27.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,現在就裝作一副失落的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.81,0:19:28.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.94,0:19:29.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你看吧 她來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:31.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,拍照的機會到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:40.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是玩具蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.57,0:19:41.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,拍的不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.57,0:19:42.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:43.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你剛才拍我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.78,0:19:47.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,等等 快刪掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:49.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不要 我好不容易才拍到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.79,0:19:53.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你要是什麼都願意做的話 我就把它刪掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.88,0:19:56.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡的高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:19:58.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個計劃也太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.84,0:20:01.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 真是拍到好照片了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.59,0:20:02.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片也要看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:04.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我就不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:05.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你看你看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:10.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,還是連拍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:12.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,很不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:14.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這表情變化
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:22.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡的高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.37,0:20:25.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.58,0:20:29.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我要把你這副咧著嘴笑得像個傻子一樣的表情拍下來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.16,0:20:33.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你肯定會羞得抬不起頭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:37.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,拍好看了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.21,0:20:40.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣一來就扯平了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:43.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哪裡扯平了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:48.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我把這張刪掉 你也把那些刪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.56,0:20:51.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我不刪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.10,0:20:53.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,所以你不刪我的照片也行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.15,0:20:57.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 我不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.03,0:21:04.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.82,0:21:08.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她心情真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.87,0:21:12.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明明我一張有趣的照片也沒拍到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.50,0:21:15.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:18.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我的照片 不可以給別人看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.80,0:21:22.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我會害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.39,0:21:34.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不不 我怎麼會給別人看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.89,0:21:37.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不知道別人會說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.02,0:21:40.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太危險了 還是刪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:48.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她說她會害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.99,0:21:52.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,說不定哪天和她談判的時候能用到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.50,0:21:57.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,先留著吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——OPJP——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.90,0:00:17.53,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}勘違いされちゃったっていいよ、君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.62,0:00:21.91,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて思ってたって言わないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.96,0:00:32.26,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}近づく空の香りを隣で感じていたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.72,0:00:41.10,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}校庭で君のことを一番に見つけて今日は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.14,0:00:49.36,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて話しかけようか？ ちょっと考えるの楽しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.40,0:00:52.32,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}風に揺らされるカーテン
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.11,0:00:57.70,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不意打ちに当たる日差し
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.78,0:01:01.58,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}眩しそうな顔を笑ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:05.50,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}照れて伏せちゃうのね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:13.59,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}憂鬱なテストも吹き飛ばせるような
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.72,0:01:21.89,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ねえ、二人で秘密の約束をしたいなって提案です
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.27,0:01:27.31,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}勘違いされちゃったっていいよ、君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.52,0:01:31.32,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて思ってたって言わないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.32,0:01:41.53,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}近づく空の香りを隣で感じていたいの
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——OPCH——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.90,0:00:17.53,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}會錯意了也沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.62,0:00:21.91,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}和你一起就是幸福 這樣想著卻不告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.96,0:00:32.26,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}瀰漫在周圍的那陣幽香 想在你的身邊靜靜感受
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.72,0:00:41.10,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}在校園的庭院 第一個發現你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.14,0:00:49.36,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}今天要和你說些什麼呢 即便是想著這些也是一種樂趣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.40,0:00:52.32,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}窗簾隨風起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.11,0:00:57.70,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不經意地投入一束陽光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.78,0:01:01.58,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你那美麗的容顏笑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:05.50,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}羞得我抬不起頭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:13.59,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}風兒喧囂 似要吹散考試的憂鬱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.72,0:01:21.89,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}吶 我想要和你一起 立下兩人的秘密約定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.27,0:01:27.31,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}會錯意了也沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.52,0:01:31.32,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}和你一起就是幸福 這樣想著卻不告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.32,0:01:41.53,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}瀰漫在周圍的那陣幽香 想在你的身邊靜靜感受
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——EDJP——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.55,0:22:15.64,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}広い宇宙の数ある一つ　青い地球の広い世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.64,0:22:24.61,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}小さな恋の思いは届く　小さな島のあなたのもとへ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.36,0:22:30.66,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}あなたと出会い　時は流れる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.91,0:22:35.33,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}思いをこめた　手紙もふえる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.50,0:22:40.25,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}いつしか二人互いに響く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.29,0:22:44.96,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}時に激しく　時に切なく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.01,0:22:49.64,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}響くは遠く　遥か彼方へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.64,0:22:54.39,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}優しい歌は　世界を変える
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.89,0:23:01.19,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ほら　あなたにとって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.65,0:23:07.20,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}大事な人ほど　すぐそばにいるの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.20,0:23:13.33,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ただあなたにだけ　届いて欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.37,0:23:16.70,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}響け恋の歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.70,0:23:25.67,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ほら　ほら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.84,0:23:35.01,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ほら　響け恋の歌
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——EDCH——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.55,0:22:15.64,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}想把這遼闊宇宙中絕無僅有的小小的相思之情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.64,0:22:24.61,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}傳達給蔚藍地球上廣闊世界中小小島嶼上的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.36,0:22:30.66,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}與你邂逅 光陰飛逝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.91,0:22:35.33,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}飽含思念的信件堆積如山
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.50,0:22:40.25,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不知不覺我們心生共鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.29,0:22:44.96,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}時而充滿激情 時而傷感不已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.01,0:22:49.64,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}迴響漸漸遠去 到那遙遠彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.64,0:22:54.39,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你那溫柔的歌聲 改變了我的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.89,0:23:01.19,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你看 對你而言
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.65,0:23:07.20,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}重要的人近在咫尺
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.20,0:23:13.33,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}只願你能感受到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.37,0:23:16.70,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}這響徹天地的戀歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.70,0:23:25.67,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你聽 你聽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.84,0:23:31.01,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}聽見了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.01,0:23:35.01,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}這響徹天地的戀歌
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——STAFF——
